    public final class ChoiceBuilder3<A,​B,​C>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ToGenerator<com.jnape.palatable.lambda.adt.choice.Choice3<A,​B,​C>>
    A builder to facilitate the construction of Generators that yield Choice3 values.

    Use one of the or(software.kes.kraftwerk.Weighted<? extends software.kes.kraftwerk.Generator<? extends D>>) methods to add more choices, and call toGenerator() to build the final Generator.

    All instances of ChoiceBuilder are immutable and can be reused, even after calling toGenerator.
